<li id="cite_note-8"><span class="mw-cite-backlink noprint"><a href="#cite_ref-8">↑</a> </span><span class="reference-text"><span class="ouvrage" id="Duprat2018"><span class="ouvrage" id="Julie_Duprat2018">Julie Duprat, «&#160;<a rel="nofollow" class="external text" href="https://minorhist.hypotheses.org/113"><cite style="font-style:normal;">Se rebeller: les esclaves marrons à Bordeaux</cite></a>&#160;», sur <span class="italique">Noire Métropole</span>, <time class="nowrap" datetime="2018-02-28" data-sort-value="2018-02-28">28 février 2018</time> <small style="line-height:1em;">(consulté le <time class="nowrap" datetime="2021-09-02" data-sort-value="2021-09-02">2 septembre 2021</time>)</small></span></span>.</span>
</li>
<li id="cite_note-9"><span class="mw-cite-backlink noprint"><a href="#cite_ref-9">↑</a> </span><span class="reference-text"><span class="ouvrage" id="Roach_et_Jürgen_Thomaneck1985"><span class="ouvrage" id="John_Roach_et_Jürgen_Thomaneck1985"><abbr class="abbr indicateur-langue" title="Langue : anglais">(en)</abbr> John Roach et Jürgen Thomaneck, <cite class="italique" lang="en">Police and public order in Europe</cite>, <time>1985</time>, 293&#160;<abbr class="abbr" title="pages">p.</abbr> <small style="line-height:1em;">(<a href="/wiki/International_Standard_Book_Number" title="International Standard Book Number">ISBN</a>&#160;<a href="/wiki/Spécial:Ouvrages_de_référence/978-0-7099-2242-1" title="Spécial:Ouvrages de référence/978-0-7099-2242-1"><span class="nowrap">978-0-7099-2242-1</span></a>, <a rel="nofollow" class="external text" href="https://books.google.co.uk/books?id=GJsOAAAAQAAJ&amp;pg=PA256&amp;dq=sweden+slavery+1335&amp;hl=en&amp;ei=rXDATMfOKZGVOtaWmf0L&amp;sa=X&amp;oi=book_result&amp;ct=result&amp;resnum=2&amp;ved=0CDIQ6AEwAQ#v=onepage&amp;q=sweden slavery 1335&amp;f=false">lire en ligne</a>)</small>, <abbr class="abbr" title="page">p.</abbr>&#160;256<span class="Z3988" title="ctx_ver=Z39.88-2004&amp;rft_val_fmt=info%3Aofi%2Ffmt%3Akev%3Amtx%3Abook&amp;rft.genre=book&amp;rft.btitle=Police+and+public+order+in+Europe&amp;rft.au=John+Roach+et+J%C3%BCrgen+Thomaneck&amp;rft.date=1985&amp;rft.pages=256&amp;rft.tpages=293&amp;rft.isbn=978-0-7099-2242-1&amp;rfr_id=info%3Asid%2Ffr.wikipedia.org%3AAbolition+de+l'esclavage"></span></span></span>.</span>
